{"id": 1099, "genre": 1000, "title": "你对所谓“文创书店”有什么不满意？", "description": "提点意见，没啥恶意，就，老担心它们付不起房租。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 4889, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160720184541ca80jxvdfU75DiTF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-25T17:00:35Z", "questions": [{"id": 980, "title": "你对所谓“文创书店”有什么不满意？", "content": "你对商场里文创书店有什么印象？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 96150, "content": "不办会员没什么折扣，办了会员又不会常去", "image": "img/option/option/20160708101113EdQMvlyRfj6nAZD7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96159, "content": "质量参差不齐，机场书随处可见", "image": "img/option/option/20160708094553FN9s34fAdSjDXtH8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96153, "content": "像用书点缀的咖啡馆，关键咖啡还不好喝", "image": "img/option/option/201607081033460zVX7RqYxHkcg24F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96154, "content": "提供的座位不够，周末总是一座难求", "image": "img/option/option/20160708094338HZBKRzPbvi2YJkyr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96155, "content": "背景音乐的品味很重要，有时候让人无法不在意", "image": "img/option/option/20160708093926ozfPLpti4rSx9qK2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96156, "content": "不同书店品牌之间没什么辨识度，卖的书都差不多", "image": "img/option/option/20160708094949S7G0TJszcj1Pl5Yk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96157, "content": "书的种类少，都是入门级，不够专业", "image": "img/option/option/20160708095013lNEcxtpg5jBK79Jw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96158, "content": "一个作者的书散落好几处，是故意Mix？", "image": "img/option/option/20160708103458ulfhn4F6rdXx9sec.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 96160, "content": "文创产品只负责美，溢价太高没什么可买的", "image": "img/option/option/20160708103014hVIE46XkxbGZqNRp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}